'''Xachibik broth''' was a thick meat, herb and spice combination enjoyed by [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiees]]. It was considered to be a delicacy. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] deemed it as a "safe" food, fit for [[Human/Legends|Human]] consumption&mdash;as many Wookiee foods were spicy enough to cause damage to a Human's gullet.

